# Fix Game Launch Targeting and Exe Not Found Errors

The goal is to ensure all games (Steam, Epic, GOG, Amazon, Custom) correctly target the selected executable and resolve "exe not found" errors, particularly with ColdClientLoader.

## Proposed Changes

### [Component] Steam Utilities
#### [MODIFY] [SteamUtils.kt](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/utils/SteamUtils.kt)
- **Robust INI Targeting**: Change `writeSteamclientLoaderIni` to ALWAYS use `A:\$executablePath` if the game is mapped to A: (standard for this app now). This bypasses symlink naming mismatches in `steamapps/common`.
- **Normalization**: Ensure `executablePath` in the INI is correctly backslash-normalized and relative to the A: drive.
- **Naming Alignment**: Ensure `gameName` used for legacy symlinks matches the actual folder name on disk to prevent breakage of legacy games.
- **ColdClientLoader Parity**: Added missing `createAppManifest`, `autoLoginUserChanges`, and `setupLightweightSteamConfig` to `replaceSteamclientDll`.

### [Component] Launch Infrastructure
#### [MODIFY] [XServerScreen.kt](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/ui/screen/xserver/XServerScreen.kt)
- **Fix Persistence Bug**: Correct the [applyToContainer](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/utils/ContainerUtils.kt#327-343) call for Steam games to use the full `appId` (e.g., `STEAM_12345`) instead of just the numeric ID. This ensures user-selected executables are actually saved and loaded.
- **Enhanced Logging**: Add detailed Timber logs for ALL game types showing the final constructed Windows command and working directory.

### [Component] GOG Service
#### [MODIFY] [GOGManager.kt](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/service/gog/GOGManager.kt)
- **Path Verification**: Add logging to verify GOG launch command correctly maps to the A: drive.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Verification
- Build debug APK: `./gradlew assembleDebug`
- Inspect logs during launch to verify command strings.

### Manual Verification
- Launch a Steam game using ColdClientLoader mode.
- Change the executable in settings and verify the launch targets the new one.
- Verify Epic/Amazon/GOG/Custom games still launch correctly with the A: drive.
